description:
A turkey secretly packed with Granny's explosive hot sauce threatens to ruin Christmas dinner for good.  Ryan is called to investigate, but is forced to bring his niece and nephew along for the mission.  Will he be able to show the rambunctious twins patience and keep his cool long enough to stop the explosion?

Director: Robert Fernandez
Starring: Chris Burnett, Marieve Herington, Akai Draco, Stephanie Nadolny, Amber Larriva, R. Bruce Elliot, Cadie Brumley, Oriana Lamas
